channel.title: Auto Cache Downloader (Please Help)
channel.description:
Her Guys, The last thing I have to do to my server is the Auto Cache Downloader. There isn't a big issue here but the cache downloads. It loads like this every time - [img]http://i.imgur.com/w2fQfVZ.png[/img]
Then when it reaches 100% this happens - [img]http://i.imgur.com/3mTQ1Wr.png[/img]
Even if I re-open the client again and again the cache will do the same as Picture 1. I have deleted the cache and tried but it doesn't work.
Can someone post below about a fix or maybe help me on Skype or Teamviewer? Thanks.
